data.title: My Family Tree
data.text:
Information on these families also came from the Hugh McArthur genealogy by Donna Phillips on the Island Register, the Dyment genealogy by Roger Dyment and Connie Ladner, and The Descendants of Henry Oliver Boulter and Maria Gard by Robert Boulter.

Children of James Boulter and Ellen MacArthur from the PEI Bap. Index were:

Albert Watson 7 Dec 1869

Amos Hubbard 13 Oct 1871

Annie Josephine 19 Sept 1879

Curtis 18 Oct 1877

Edmund 8 July 1875

James Bertram 17 Oct 1867 - no place of birth given

All were born in Pierre Jacques, Lot 6.
